projects.description:
Europeana Cloud is changing the way that data is sent to Europeana, and giving researchers new tools to enrich and use that data.  Our new cloud-based infrastructure will make it possible for:
-  Content providers and aggregators to efficiently store, share and provide access to digital cultural heritage;
-  Researchers to work on the content with new services and tools;
-  Everyone to feed back enriched data back into the cloud, for use by institutions and researchers alike.
